{"tid":137333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每天都暈船...4年前玩太空山後「永久暈眩」　她怒告迪士尼","createTime":"2017-02-27T17:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T18:18:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1aaaa39f13489e24475695172b0f4a0817043814","tid":137333,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1377/d1377563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1377%2Fd1377563.jpg&h=d5c6a258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">▲迪士尼樂園的「飛越太空山」雲霄飛車。（圖／翻攝自Disneyland）</span><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n法國一名27歲女子，近日對迪士尼樂園提出告訴，因為她4年前搭乘迪士尼招牌遊樂設施「太空山」（Space Mountain）後就罹患「登陸困難症」，每天都像是搭船一般暈眩不止，還被認定為殘疾人士，在也無法正常工作，因此憤而向迪士尼求償。<br />\n《國際財經時報》（International Business Times）引述《泰晤士報》（The Times）報導，現年27歲的法國女子在2013年造訪迪士尼樂園，不料搭乘知名雲霄飛車「太空山」之後，她每天都覺得頭暈目眩，「就像是每天都在搭船一樣」。<br />\n女子被醫師診斷出罹患「登陸困難症」（MdDS），一般好發在乘船回到陸地上的人。女子說，她每天都飽受永久性暈眩所苦，甚至不能再抱自己的兒子，因為可能會把他摔到地上。另外，她也必須放棄跳舞、騎車等愛好。<br />\n原本在銀行上班的她，幾乎沒有辦法再工作，領取到殘障手冊後才勉強獲得留職。她的律師宣稱，2015年時迪士尼曾提出賠償2萬9950歐元（約台幣97萬）的條件和解，但律師指稱，這個數字「根本不夠」。<br />\n律師請求法院進行醫學檢驗，要證明女子的症狀是因為迪士尼「太空山」所引起。迪士尼則否認曾提出和解，僅表示「案件正在進行中，無法評論」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 每天都暈船...4年前玩太空山後「永久暈眩」　她怒告迪士尼 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday 新聞雲 <a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170228/874751.htm#ixzz4ZuNLhmxB \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170228%2F874751.htm%23ixzz4ZuNLhmxB%20&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4b745d5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170228/874751.htm#ixzz4ZuNLhmxB </a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"4cfae291cc48b335e9b056649a6d093e82d868fe","tid":137333,"uid":61735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a19a295416dfc359c86dbef1bdf52f0626a3998","tid":137333,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"咁撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9883c90300b4bd244279484b9c785eba7a5f672a","tid":137333,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"玩多幾次"},{"pid":"6e38225df8b6d5ce74047d139f5524fc1bedfc99","tid":137333,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"MDDS真係無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係靠自己修復"},{"pid":"774bae890f8e3972d5be38ece4b8ab99f4bde46a","tid":137333,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:16:32.000Z","msg":"去行船囉<br />\n一轉返嚟乜都慣"},{"pid":"f1f173bdf38dc01e71db9ec08bd71662209371cf","tid":137333,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去行船囉<br />\n一轉返嚟乜都慣</blockquote><br />\n以毒攻毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1256112c2dbc0ffb6761f681786947b025ffbf49","tid":137333,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:18:35.000Z","msg":"渣ga"}]}